Suddenly, a shimmer crawls across her skin — delicate pink crystals begin to form along her jawline, spreading in thin, translucent layers across her face, neck, hands, and even her jacket, like frost kissed with rose light. Rendered in a hyperreal neon-pop style with pastel crystal overlays and cinematic close-up detailing, the scene becomes a vibrant fusion of glam rebellion and quiet metamorphosis.
